# 🚀 Personal Portfolio

A modern, responsive **Portfolio Website** built using **React.js** and **TailwindCSS**.  
It highlights my **skills**, **projects**, and provides ways to **connect** with me.

---

## 📄 Features

- Fully responsive design (Mobile / Tablet / Desktop)
- Built with **React** for a component-based structure
- Styled using **TailwindCSS** for fast and clean UI
- Smooth animations and transitions
- Showcases my **projects**, **skills**, and **contact links**
- Easy to maintain and extend

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **React.js**
- **TailwindCSS**
- **Framer Motion** (optional, for animations)
- **React Icons** (for social/media icons)

